    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Public buildings in the United Kingdom that house various county functions, often comprising a large hall for public meetings and rooms for county courts and administration; for structures housing similar judicial functions in the United States, use "county courthouses."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
